  - When: Reconcile() called\n335:   - Then: Pod created with sidecar container\n336: \n337: #### Unit Tests - SandboxProcessor\n338: \n339: - [ ] **TEST-010**: `TestSandboxProcessor_BuildSandboxPod` in `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/sandbox_processor_test.go`\n340:   - Given: AgentRuntime with full spec\n341:   - When: BuildSandboxPod() called\n342:   - Then: Pod has correct name, labels, owner reference, container spec\n343: \n344: - [ ] **TEST-011**: `TestSandboxProcessor_BuildSandboxPod_WithCodeInterpreter`\n345:   - Given: AgentRuntime with CodeInterpreter enabled\n346:   - When: BuildSandboxPod() called\n347:   - Then: Pod has sidecar container\n348: \n349: - [ ] **TEST-012**: `TestSandboxProcessor_NeedsUpdate_ImageChanged`\n350:   - Given: Pod with old image, AgentRuntime with new image\n351:   - When: NeedsUpdate() called\n352:   - Then: Returns true\n353: \n354: - [ ] **TEST-013**: `TestSandboxProcessor_NeedsUpdate_NoChange`\n355:   - Given: Pod matches AgentRuntime spec\n356:   - When: NeedsUpdate() called\n357:   - Then: Returns false\n358: \n359: - [ ] **TEST-014**: `TestSandboxProcessor_UpdateSandboxPod`\n360:   - Given: Pod needs update\n361:   - When: UpdateSandboxPod() called\n362:   - Then: Old pod deleted, new pod created\n363: \n364: #### Unit Tests - StatusUpdater\n365: \n366: - [ ] **TEST-015**: `TestStatusUpdater_UpdateAgentRuntimeStatus_PodRunning` in `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/status_updater_test.go`\n367:   - Given: AgentRuntime with running pod\n368:   - When: UpdateAgentRuntimeStatus() called\n369:   - Then: Status.Phase=Running, SandboxRef set, Endpoint set\n370: \n371: - [ ] **TEST-016**: `TestStatusUpdater_UpdateAgentRuntimeStatus_PodPending`\n372:   - Given: AgentRuntime with pending pod\n373:   - When: UpdateAgentRuntimeStatus() called\n374:   - Then: Status.Phase=Pending\n375: \n376: - [ ] **TEST-017**: `TestStatusUpdater_UpdateAgentRuntimeStatus_NoChange`\n377:   - Given: Status unchanged\n378:   - When: UpdateAgentRuntimeStat