{"type":"text","timestamp":1775846853941,"sessionID":"ses_28747d297ffexyaGlTcDQblQ3b","part":{"id":"prt_d78b87314001E7498TbWQZ4vd5","messageID":"msg_d78b8653f001kyZzvWhbsj3iah","sessionID":"ses_28747d297ffexyaGlTcDQblQ3b","type":"text","text":"The existing `tasks.md` file at `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-008/tasks.md` is already complete and comprehensive. It contains 267 lines with:\n\n- **7 phases** with 42 tasks\n- **31 test cases** covering unit, integration, and infrastructure tests\n- **4 documentation tasks**\n- **12 acceptance criteria**\n- Dependencies section\n\nThe checklist is well-structured following the same pattern as AR-007 and AR-006. Here's a summary:\n\n**Phases:**\n1. GC Policy & Configuration (TASK-001 to 004)\n2. GC Core Logic (TASK-010 to 017)\n3. Activity Tracking (TASK-020 to 023)\n4. Metrics (TASK-030 to 032)\n5. Configuration Integration (TASK-040 to 042)\n6. Testing - TDD (TEST-001 to TEST-051)\n7. Documentation (DOC-001 to DOC-004)\n\n**Key Features Covered:**\n- GC configuration with Enabled/Interval/IdleTimeout/MaxIdleCount/DryRun\n- Sandbox state machine (Active/Idle/Orphaned/Expired)\n- Periodic GC with ticker-based scheduling\n- Activity tracking integration\n- Prometheus metrics\n- Flag and env var configuration\n- Comprehensive test coverage (>0.5 ratio target)\n- Graceful shutdown\n\nThe tasks.md is ready for implementation.","time":{"start":1775846853940,"end":1775846853940}}}
